  <summary date="2025-03-04T19:00:22Z" status="Introduced in House">TSA Commuting Fairness Act

This bill directs the Transportation Security Administration (TSA) to submit to Congress a study on the feasibility of treating as on-duty hours the time TSA employees working at airport locations spend traveling between regular duty locations, airport parking lots,&#160;and bus and transit stops.</summary>
